Tony's raised hand is all that's
coming between the tussling Lions

00:06:14.629 --> 00:06:21.629
and a blast from the fire
extinguishers.

00:06:51.060 --> 00:06:54.379
Bella's turn to make the first move

00:07:19.979 --> 00:07:23.759
"She's

00:07:23.759 --> 00:07:27.499
not rushing back to him so that's good.

00:07:27.499 --> 00:07:30.639
We might just let him go back for tonight

00:07:30.639 --> 00:07:34.210
and try again in the morning.

00:07:34.210 --> 00:07:37.260
So, we haven't the perfect scenario of two

00:07:37.260 --> 00:07:41.590
lions together, so what we're going to do,
tomorrow morning we're going to come back

00:07:41.590 --> 00:07:44.589
and

00:07:44.589 --> 00:07:46.740
do a much softer

00:07:46.740 --> 00:07:49.680
introduction by releasing her into the
outside,

00:07:49.680 --> 00:07:53.580
opening his den and letting him follow her.
We feel that

00:07:53.580 --> 00:07:57.840
outside will give them a more natural advantage

00:07:57.840 --> 00:08:04.840
and make them feel more relaxed."

00:08:44.380 --> 00:08:48.529
Once bitten, twice shy, Simba refuses

00:08:48.529 --> 00:08:52.589
to venture outside.

00:08:52.589 --> 00:08:53.269
are lions

00:08:53.269 --> 00:08:57.589
which for most of their lives have been alone. Simba has never,

00:08:57.589 --> 00:09:00.709
ever met another female, probably in his whole life.

00:09:00.709 --> 00:09:03.720
This is actually the first time he has met a female,

00:09:03.720 --> 00:09:09.250
so it's not very strange that he takes his time"

00:09:36.740 --> 00:09:39.790
A new day and Tony has a new plan.

00:09:39.790 --> 00:09:42.809
"The only way we can get him to come
outside

00:09:42.809 --> 00:09:47.459
was to let him go out into his
territory first. We then

00:09:47.459 --> 00:09:50.569
released her into his territory.

00:09:50.569 --> 00:09:53.779
So, we took a chance and

00:09:53.779 --> 00:10:00.779
the result is this."

00:10:00.860 --> 00:10:03.720
"We have a situation where the animals
laying, probably

00:10:03.720 --> 00:10:06.950
less than 3 meters appart and

00:10:06.950 --> 00:10:11.580
although I'm there is tension there..."

00:10:19.980 --> 00:10:23.590
"This is a natural progression

00:10:23.590 --> 00:10:30.250
to lions becoming accustomed to each
other.

00:10:30.250 --> 00:10:34.230
I'm exceedingly happy and so are all the staff at Lilongwe

00:10:34.230 --> 00:10:41.230
and it appears that it's all going to turn out really well."

